Yeep, y-yeep?! {短暂停}
Yeeeeep!
Oh my... This is quite the remarkable discovery!

Huh?{短暂停}—Huh?
Is it really that intense?{短暂停}
...I need to take another look.

Like blue paintbrushes, green paintbrushes, pink paintbrushes,
purple crystal hairpins, green Christmas stockings{短暂停}
and such...

If your friends happen to find any{短暂停}
lost items,
could you ask them to let me examine them?

Yesterday, I tried those shrub leaves{短暂停}
that I gave to Mr. Mobai.
They make quite a nice tea~.

...{思考}
Beyond my comprehension...
How can someone be closer than family? What does that even mean?

Your friend is quite the chatterbox,
And keeps circling around me incessantly.{短暂停}
Tell me... how long has your companion been exhibiting these symptoms?

Oh, so you two are classmates!
Having companions by your side during these wonderful years...{短暂停}
As for me, I'm quite different!~

Your friends who visit seem to look different each time...
{短暂停}
Just how many friends do you have?
